<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Appointment Reminder - TechTrainers</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #292524;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #fafaf9;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #2563eb 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        .header p {
            margin: 10px 0 0 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 30px;
        }
        
        .appointment-card {
            background: #f0f9ff;
            border: 1px solid #bae6fd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .appointment-detail {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #bae6fd;
        }
        
        .appointment-detail:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
            margin-bottom: 0;
            padding-bottom: 0;
        }
        
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1e40af;
            min-width: 120px;
        }
        
        .detail-value {
            color: #1e293b;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .countdown-timer {
            background: #fef3c7;
            border: 1px solid #fcd34d;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .countdown-timer h3 {
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            color: #92400e;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        
        .countdown-number {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #d97706;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        
        .trainer-info {
            background: #f8fafc;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .trainer-info h3 {
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            color: #374151;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .action-buttons {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            margin: 0 10px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .btn-primary {
            background: #3b82f6;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .btn-secondary {
            background: #6b7280;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .btn-danger {
            background: #ef4444;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-1px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }
        
        .footer {
            background: #292524;
            color: #a8a29e;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .footer a {
            color: #d97706;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        
        .divider {
            height: 1px;
            background: #e2e8f0;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .reminder-badge {
            background: #dbeafe;
            color: #1e40af;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        .preparation-checklist {
            background: #f0fdf4;
            border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .preparation-checklist h3 {
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            color: #166534;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .checklist-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .checklist-item input[type="checkbox"] {
            margin-right: 8px;
            transform: scale(1.2);
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 0;
                border-radius: 0;
            }
            
            .content {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            
            .header {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            
            .btn {
                display: block;
                margin: 10px 0;
            }
            
            .countdown-number {
                font-size: 28px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>‚è∞ Appointment Reminder</h1>
            <p>Your training session is coming up soon!</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hi <strong>{{clientName}}</strong>,</p>
            
            <p>This is a friendly reminder that your training session is scheduled for <strong>{{reminderTime}}</strong>. We're excited to help you reach your fitness goals! üí™</p>
            
            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;">
                <span class="reminder-badge">‚è∞ Reminder</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="countdown-timer">
                <h3>‚è≥ Time Until Your Session</h3>
                <div class="countdown-number">{{hoursUntilSession}}</div>
                <p>{{hoursUntilSession}} {{#eq hoursUntilSession 1}}hour{{else}}hours{{/eq}} remaining</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="appointment-card">
                <div class="appointment-detail">
                    <span class="detail-label">üìÖ Date:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{appointmentDate}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="appointment-detail">
                    <span class="detail-label">‚è∞ Time:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{appointmentTime}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="appointment-detail">
                    <span class="detail-label">üí™ Session Type:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{sessionType}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="appointment-detail">
                    <span class="detail-label">‚è±Ô∏è Duration:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{duration}} minutes</span>
                </div>
                <div class="appointment-detail">
                    <span class="detail-label">üìç Location:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{location}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="appointment-detail">
                    <span class="detail-label">üè∑Ô∏è Booking ID:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{bookingId}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="trainer-info">
                <h3>üèãÔ∏è Your Personal Trainer</h3>
                <div class="appointment-detail">
                    <span class="detail-label">Name:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{trainerName}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="appointment-detail">
                    <span class="detail-label">Contact:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{trainerPhone}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="appointment-detail">
                    <span class="detail-label">Specialization:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{trainerSpecialization}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="preparation-checklist">
                <h3>üìù Pre-Session Checklist</h3>
                <div class="checklist-item">
                    <input type="checkbox" id="clothes" disabled>
                    <label for="clothes">Pack comfortable workout clothes</label>
                </div>
                <div class="checklist-item">
                    <input type="checkbox" id="water" disabled>
                    <label for="water">Bring water bottle</label>
                </div>
                <div class="checklist-item">
                    <input type="checkbox" id="towel" disabled>
                    <label for="towel">Pack a towel</label>
                </div>
                <div class="checklist-item">
                    <input type="checkbox" id="snack" disabled>
                    <label for="snack">Light snack (if needed)</label>
                </div>
                <div class="checklist-item">
                    <input type="checkbox" id="shoes" disabled>
                    <label for="shoes">Proper athletic shoes</label>
                </div>
                <div class="checklist-item">
                    <input type="checkbox" id="arrival" disabled>
                    <label for="arrival">Plan to arrive 5-10 minutes early</label>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="action-buttons">
                <a href="{{confirmAttendanceUrl}}" class="btn btn-primary">‚úÖ Confirm Attendance</a>
                <a href="{{rescheduleUrl}}" class="btn btn-secondary">üìÖ Reschedule</a>
                <a href="{{cancelUrl}}" class="btn btn-danger">‚ùå Cancel</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="divider"></div>
            
            <p><strong>üìç Location Details:</strong></p>
            <p>{{locationDetails}}</p>
            <p><strong>Parking:</strong> {{parkingInfo}}</p>
            
            <p><strong>üí° Pro Tips for Your Session:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Eat a light meal 1-2 hours before your session</li>
                <li>Stay hydrated throughout the day</li>
                <li>Get a good night's sleep before your workout</li>
                <li>Communicate any injuries or concerns to your trainer</li>
                <li>Bring a positive mindset and be ready to challenge yourself!</li>
            </ul>
            
            <div class="divider"></div>
            
            <p><strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Important:</strong> If you need to cancel or reschedule, please do so at least 24 hours in advance to avoid any cancellation fees.</p>
            
            <p>Questions or need to make changes? Contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a> or call <a href="tel:{{supportPhone}}">{{supportPhone}}</a>.</p>
            
            <p>We're looking forward to an amazing session with you!</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>
            <strong>The TechTrainers Team</strong></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>
                <strong>TechTrainers</strong> - Empowering Fitness Through Technology<br>
                <a href="{{companyWebsite}}">{{companyWebsite}}</a> | 
                <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a><br>
                <a href="{{manageAppointmentsUrl}}">Manage Appointments</a> | 
                <a href="{{unsubscribeUrl}}">Unsubscribe</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>